          </table></p><p>The change in the resource element of the DEL arises from the partial take up of &#x00A3;713,000 end year flexibility, of which &#x00A3;472,000 is required for additional consultancy, &#x00A3;91,000 for legal costs and &#x00A3;150,000 for an extension to the twinning with Poland programme under the EU's PHARE initiative. The increase will be offset by a corresponding increase in appropriations in aid.</p><p><table>
          <tr>
          <td>Resources (&#x00A3;000)</td>
